229
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:15,919
Water...

230
00:12:16,559 --> 00:12:17,440
There's water ahead.

231
00:12:18,399 --> 00:12:19,120
I left marks...

232
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:19,879
Erfeng.

233
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,200
What did you leave?

234
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,120
Marks?

235
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:23,240
Erfeng.

236
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:24,480
Don't scare me, Erfeng.

237
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,320
Erfeng!

238
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,600
Marks...

239
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:31,000
Erfeng.

240
00:12:32,679 --> 00:12:33,200
Marks...

241
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,200
She must have left marks.

242
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,279
Erfeng, hang in there.

243
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:39,799
I'll find you soon.

244
00:12:40,279 --> 00:12:41,840
Hold on, don't panic.

245
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:43,919
Marks.

246
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:47,919
Cross...

247
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,120
Go left.

248
00:12:50,279 --> 00:12:50,799
Erfeng.

249
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,080
Erfeng.

250
00:12:55,639 --> 00:12:56,799
-Erfeng!
-Jinbai!

251
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,720
Erfeng, where are you?

252
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:04,840
Horizontal means back.

253
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:05,960
Erfeng.

254
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,120
I'm coming, don't worry.

255
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:12,039
Erfeng.

256
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:13,759
Erfeng.

257
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,080
Erfeng.

258
00:13:17,879 --> 00:13:18,639
Erfeng.

259
00:13:18,639 --> 00:13:19,720
Vertical means forward.

260
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,639
Horizontal means back.

261
00:13:20,639 --> 00:13:22,320
It's my little distress signal.

262
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,120
Erfeng, where are you, Erfeng?

263
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,200
Erfeng!

264
00:13:25,279 --> 00:13:25,840
Erfeng!

265
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:28,159
Erfeng, where are you, Erfeng?

266
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:30,480
Cross means left.

267
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,480
Plus sign means right.

268
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,080
Erfeng.

269
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,080
Can you hear me, Erfeng?

270
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:53,399
Jinbai.

271
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:54,480
You're awake.

272
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,440
It's okay, we're going back now.

273
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:06,960
Jinbai.

274
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:10,200
I knew you would find me.

275
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:15,759
Shen Jiaqin.

276
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:17,679
Hmm?

277
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:18,600
It's me.

278
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,200
I'm sorry.

279
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,559
I just had a dream.

280
00:14:26,159 --> 00:14:27,240
I dreamed...

281
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,399
