282
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,440
Jinbai saved me.

283
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,799
So I just...

284
00:14:35,799 --> 00:14:36,840
No 'so'.

285
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:38,960
As long as you're safe,

286
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,159
I'm fine with anything.

287
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:43,759
Sleep now.

288
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,080
We'll be there soon.

289
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:51,720
Boss.

290
00:14:52,159 --> 00:14:52,600
Boss.

291
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,480
