292
00:14:54,279 --> 00:14:54,720
I'm back.

293
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:56,440
Shanshan! Shanshan, are you okay?

294
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,600
Let me.

295
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,879
How are you? Are you okay?

296
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,639
Jinbai.

297
00:15:37,759 --> 00:15:38,360
You're awake.

298
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:43,840
Want some hot water?

299
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:48,360
Was it you who found me?

300
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,000
It was Shen Jiaqin.

301
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,039
How could it be Shen Jiaqin?

302
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,000
Jinbai.

303
00:16:00,399 --> 00:16:01,919
Do you remember...

304
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,320
that time during our graduation camping trip?

305
00:16:04,879 --> 00:16:05,720
I got lost then too.

306
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,200
Of course I remember.

307
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,960
I was just thinking about that.

308
00:16:10,399 --> 00:16:11,960
I found you in the woods.

309
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,120
And carried you back.

310
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,399
Where did you find me?

311
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:22,320
I remember it was under a big tree...

312
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,360
next to the campsite entrance.

313
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:26,960
But that's not right.

314
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:29,240
After we took the graduation photo,

315
00:16:29,519 --> 00:16:30,759
on my way to find him

316
00:16:30,759 --> 00:16:31,919
I accidentally fell.

317
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,919
Later, I was exhausted...

318
00:16:33,919 --> 00:16:35,519
and passed out next to a large rock.

319
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,720
But he found me under a tree.

320
00:16:39,279 --> 00:16:40,519
So who moved me...

321
00:16:40,519 --> 00:16:42,120
to the tree at the campsite entrance?

322
00:16:42,519 --> 00:16:45,039
Did you see my marks back then?

323
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,360
What marks?

324
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:55,720
Vertical means forward.

325
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,519
Horizontal means back.

326
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,559
Cross means left.

327
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,080
Plus sign means right.

328
00:17:01,519 --> 00:17:02,200
What does that mean?

329
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:05,000
He doesn't know my bandage distress signals.

330
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:07,599
So the one who used the marks to find me...

331
00:17:07,599 --> 00:17:08,599
and moved me from the rock...

332
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:10,720
to under the tree was someone else.

333
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,160
Maybe I remembered wrong.

334
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:18,759
Has the person who attacked me been caught?

335
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:20,440
Not yet.

336
00:17:20,759 --> 00:17:22,599
The production team said he was a temp worker...

337
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:23,799
who used a fake ID to get in.

338
00:17:24,519 --> 00:17:25,480
But don't worry,

339
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,359
the police have been notified.

340
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:27,440
They'll catch him.

341
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,599
The water seems a bit cold.

342
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,240
Let me boil another pot for you.

343
00:17:33,599 --> 00:17:34,119
Thanks.

344
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,359
Strange.

345
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:43,200
He doesn't know my bandage distress signals.

346
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,839
Then who could it be?

347
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,440
Could it be Shen Jiaqin?

348
00:17:58,279 --> 00:17:59,119
Vertical means forward.

349
00:17:59,799 --> 00:18:00,519
Horizontal means back.

350
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:01,359
Cross means left.

351
00:18:02,119 --> 00:18:02,920
Plus sign means right.

352
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:07,480
Erfeng.

353
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:08,599
Erfeng.

354
00:18:15,759 --> 00:18:16,920
Erfeng.

355
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:19,160
Erfeng, where are you?

356
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,119
Erfeng.

357
00:18:23,759 --> 00:18:24,440
Erfeng.

358
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:27,920
Erfeng.

359
00:18:36,559 --> 00:18:38,720
So it was Shen Jiaqin all along.
